---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import ContactButton from "../components/ContactButton.astro";
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<Layout>
  <div class="container mx-auto p-4">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-ebony mb-8 text-center">Services</h1>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <img
            class="w-12 h-12 mr-4"
            src="../../public/assets/img/6.png"
            alt="DEV Engineer"
          />
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ebony">DEV Engineer</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="text-ebony leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            <strong>Frontend Development:</strong> Creation of modern and responsive
            user interfaces using HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, and React. Designing intuitive
            and engaging user experiences.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Backend Development:</strong> Building APIs and backend services
            with Node.js and Python, ensuring optimal performance and scalability.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>System Integration:</strong> Connecting frontend and backend
            applications, ensuring smooth and efficient communication between components.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Web Application Development:</strong> Developing complete web
            applications, from conception to implementation, using modern technologies
            and best practices.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-10">
          <ContactButton />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <img
            class="w-12 h-12 mr-4"
            src="../../public/assets/img/5.png"
            alt="QA Engineer"
          />
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ebony">QA Engineer</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="text-ebony leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            <strong>Manual Testing:</strong> Execution of thorough tests to ensure
            software quality, including functional, regression, and user acceptance
            testing (UAT).
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Test Automation:</strong> Development of automation scripts using
            tools like Playwright, Cypress, and Selenium, optimizing testing processes
            and increasing coverage.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Automation with UiPath:</strong> Implementation of Robotic Process
            Automation (RPA) solutions to optimize workflows and reduce execution
            times.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Integration Testing:</strong> Validation of data consistency
            and interoperability between different systems and platforms.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Production Support:</strong> Identification and resolution of
            bugs in production environments, ensuring software stability and performance.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>QA Consulting:</strong> Advising on the implementation of testing
            and automation strategies, ensuring software quality from the early stages
            of development.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-10">
          <ContactButton />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
